Class MetadataUtil

java.lang.Object
  org.siframework.abbi.api.xds.MetadataUtil

public class MetadataUtil
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides a variety of utility methods to translate between XDS metadata types supported in OHT and native java types.

Parameters:
iString - The InternationStringType from which a display string is selected.
l - The locale to use when selecting the String, or null if the default locale should be used.
Returns:
The appropriate string to display for the specified locale.

asString

public static java.lang.String asString(CodedMetadataType code)
Convert a CodedMetadataType to a String. This function puts the components of the CodedMetadataType into a string in the order code|SchemeUUID|displayName|SchemeName

Parameters:
code - The CodedMetadataType to convert to a string
Returns:
A string representing the CodedMetadataType
